cs.CV, cs.GR, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.GT 

This paper is likely to belong to the computer vision (cs.CV) category as it deals with image synthesis and relighting. It may also belong to the graphics (cs.GR) category as it involves modeling the physical rendering process. The use of neural networks suggests that it could also belong to the machine learning (cs.LG) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI) categories. Finally, the paper's focus on free-viewpoint relighting suggests that it could also belong to the computer graphics (cs.GT) category.
